Class : It is a user-define non-primitive data type which represent a blue print of an object and provide all the specification of the object.
      
      "Form the above statement we can say that a class is used to create a object."

 *How to craete a class or a empty blue print :

 Syntax :
          class ClassName
            {

            }

  Example :
          class Shoe
            {

            }
